name: Goddess in the Blockchain
description:
"Goddess in the Blockchain," 2022, MP4 Video, 9s
When I lost faith in finding the Goddess in our physical world, I turned to the void of the digital world.  I explored that void until I found the deepest absence possible...and when I did, I found her.  
...I found Goddess in the blockchain.
